          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true">Opens the </text><text styleclass="Program Feature" translate="true">Live Update</text><text styleclass="Popup Box" translate="true"> facility, which will contact the Object Arts website to check for available Dolphin Smalltalk updates.</text></para>
        </td>
